    "subType": "trait",
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Inuzuka clan is a product of the Fire Country, namely Konohagakure, is a family of shinobi known for their use of ninken (ninja dogs) as fighting companions and are easily identified by the distinctive red fang markings on their cheeks.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Inuzuka Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Chakra Control, Climb, Genjutsu, Handle Animal, Intimidate, Knowledge (earth and life sciences), Knowledge (Ninja Lore), Listen, Ninjutsu, Sense Motive, Survival, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Child of the Wild), Alertness, Brawl, Chakra Restoration, Combat Martial Arts, Combat Tactics, Defensive Martial Arts, Improved Chakra Pool, Ninjutsu Adept, Nin Weapon Proficiency, Taijutsu Adept, Track.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Inuzuka Hijutsu techniques.</p>"
    },
